    <item>
      <title>迪拜公司未能逃脱“影子舰队”制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/dubai-ship-firm-sanctioned-by-uk-denies-role-in-putin-s-shadow-fleet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家总部位于迪拜的航运公司因涉嫌成为俄罗斯影子船队的一部分而成为目标，该公司在法院要求暂停英国制裁的诉讼中败诉，这是对与油价上限相关案件的首次公开质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/dubai-ship-firm-sanctioned-by-uk-denies-role-in-putin-s-shadow-fleet</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:02:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯的备用炼油能力可以减轻无人机攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/russia-s-spare-refining-capacity-seen-mitigating-drone-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的无人机袭击了占俄罗斯炼油能力十分之一以上的设施，但原油加工的实际减少量可能只有这个规模的一半，因为该国的下游工业可以利用系统中现有的闲置资源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/russia-s-spare-refining-capacity-seen-mitigating-drone-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:06:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强抵消供应紧张迹象，油价稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强抑制了投资者对大宗商品的兴趣，抵消了全球原油市场趋紧的迹象，油价稳定在每桶 81 美元附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 23:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
